<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-giJF6kkoqNQ00vy+HMDP7azOuL0xtbfIcaT9wjKHr8RbDVddVHyTfAAsrekwKmP1" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>Mega Forums</title>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <h4>MegaForums</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/posts">Posts</a></li>
            {{#if user}}
                <li><a href="/profile">Profile</a></li>
                <li><a href="/auth/logout">Log Out</a></li>
            {{else}}
                <li><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
                <li><a href="/signup">Sign Up</a></li>
            {{/if}}
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <div class="card" style="width: 36rem;display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 50px;">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Welcome to MegaForums!</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
                Welcome to MegaForums! Here you can post anything and everything. Posting requires you to log in first. Although you have to log in, everything you send on this site will be anonymous.
            </p>
            <p class="card-text">
                After you have logged in, head to the Profile page and start posting! If you aren't a member yet, click on Sign Up and make yourself a completely free profile!
            </p>
            <p class="card-text">
                We live in a world where there are rules and rules that apply here are:
            </p>
            <p class="card-text">
                1. No racism of any kind.
            <p class="card-text">
                2. Be nice to each other (banter is allowed).
            </p>
            <p class="card-text">
                3. There is a character limit on the post. Keep it simple!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>